QuestData.Title: Continued Efforts: Seeker's Quorum
QuestData.Description:
The onslaught from Zovaal's forces continues to devastate these lands.
We must send them a message. Show them we will not back down, $n.
The might of Ardenweald stands with you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Repel the Jailer's forces from Seeker's Quorum in Korthia.
